previously published in quarto

00:07:18.050 --> 00:07:21.970 position:56%
and I see plays that were never
previously published, making a total

00:07:21.970 --> 00:07:25.630
of thirty-six and establishing
Shakespeare's cannon.

00:07:25.630 --> 00:07:29.160
Though that cannon did
end up in various ways

00:07:29.160 --> 00:07:31.800
from the later 70s century
through to the present day,

00:07:31.800 --> 00:07:35.510
when the attribution Phyllis
