00:07:44.330 --> 00:07:49.550
to be a revised, but
unauthorised Shakespeare's play.

00:07:49.550 --> 00:07:54.980
So, the second, which was
published in 1632 was edited

00:07:54.980 --> 00:08:00.220
to include minor updates of
spelling and punctuation.

00:08:00.220 --> 00:08:05.020
The third, 1663 is significant,
because it was published just

00:08:05.020 --> 00:08:08.310
after the restoration of the
monarchy, meant that the theatres,

00:08:08.310 --> 00:08:12.060
which of course had been shut
for nearly 20 years had reopened

00:08:12.060 --> 00:08:15.420
