immediate predeceases.

00:11:58.450 --> 00:12:02.590
Alexander Pope's addition
followed in 1725,

00:12:02.590 --> 00:12:05.390
an in addition the quickly
attracted controversy

00:12:05.390 --> 00:12:07.730
