further than Road,

00:12:07.730 --> 00:12:12.320 position:56%
in correcting Shakespeare's text,
in a move that we might say benignly

00:12:12.320 --> 00:12:15.710
as one major poet reproducing
another,

00:12:15.710 --> 00:12:18.280
in line with the literary
taste that prevailed,

00:12:18.280 --> 00:12:20.480
