00:12:20.480 --> 00:12:23.270
Apart from Pope, the most famous
writer who edited Shakespeare

00:12:23.270 --> 00:12:26.670
in the eighteenth century
was of course Samuel Johnson.

00:12:26.670 --> 00:12:30.880
Johnson 1765 edition became
famous for his commentary

00:12:30.880 --> 00:12:36.180
and his much-quoted preface,
