00:12:49.390 --> 00:12:52.320
Johnson exemplified the idea
that I have been suggesting,

00:12:52.320 --> 00:12:56.650
is reflected in 18 century
editing, practices in general.

00:12:56.650 --> 00:12:59.620
That is that Shakespeare
needs to be extracted

00:12:59.620 --> 00:13:03.820
from his historical context and
helped by editors to be confirmed

00:13:03.820 --> 00:13:08.660
as universal, as not of
an age but for all time.

00:13:08.660 --> 00:13:12.800
Johnson's addition was revised
